  <h1>uview-plus Layout布局组件</h1>
      <p>
        uview-plus的Layout布局组件基于12分栏系统，方便开发者快速创建布局。若需宫格布局，建议使用功能更完善灵活的uview-plus
        Grid宫格组件。
      </p>

      <h2>平台支持情况</h2>
      <div class="table-container">
        <div class="table-row table-header">
          <div class="table-cell">App（vue）</div>
          <div class="table-cell">App（nvue）</div>
          <div class="table-cell">H5</div>
          <div class="table-cell">小程序</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="table-cell">√</div>
          <div class="table-cell">√</div>
          <div class="table-cell">√</div>
          <div class="table-cell">√</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>基本使用</h2>
      <p>通过`col`组件的`span`属性设置分栏比例。示例代码如下：</p>
      <pre><code class="language-html">&lt;template&gt;
      &lt;view class="u-page"&gt;
          &lt;view class="u-demo-block"&gt;
              &lt;text class="u-demo-block__title"&gt;基础使用&lt;/text&gt;
              &lt;view class="u-demo-block__content"&gt;
                  &lt;up-row customStyle="margin-bottom: 10px"&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="6"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple-light"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="6"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                  &lt;/up-row&gt;
                  &lt;up-row customStyle="margin-bottom: 10px"&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="4"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="4"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple-light"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="4"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple-dark"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                  &lt;/up-row&gt;
                  &lt;up-row justify="space-between"&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="3"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="3"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple-light"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="3"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                      &lt;up-col span="3"&gt;
                          &lt;view class="demo-layout bg-purple-light"&gt;&lt;/view&gt;
                      &lt;/up-col&gt;
                  &lt;/up-row&gt;
              &lt;/view&gt;
          &lt;/view&gt;
      &lt;/view&gt;
  &lt;/template&gt;
  
  &lt;style lang="scss"&gt;
  .wrap &#123;
      padding: 12px;
  &#125;
  .demo-layout &#123;
      height: 25px;
